      <tr class='proposal_row' id='proposal_row_525'>
        <td rowspan='2' class='description'>
          <h3>
            <a href="../../../users/me/favorites" class="favorite favorite_525"><span>*</span></a>
            
              <a href="../../../sessions/525" class="title">OSWALD: Lessons from and for the Open Hardware Movement</a>
            
            
          </h3>

          <div class="excerpt">
            Envisioned as a cutting-edge computing platform that would encourage students to tinker with all the latest developments in the mobile space without fear of breaking their own gadgets, the initial version of the OSWALD project out of OSU failed in several key areas.
	    <a href="http://linuxplumbersconf.com/2011/ocw//system/presentations/525/original/oswald_lpc-2011.pdf">(slides)</a>
          </div>
	  
        </td>

        
