      <tr class='proposal_row' id='proposal_row_435'>
        <td rowspan='2' class='description'>
          <h3>
            <a href="../../../users/me/favorites" class="favorite favorite_435"><span>*</span></a>
            
              <a href="../../../proposals/435" class="title">PEOPLE LOAD BALANCING - SKILL BASED PROJECT MANAGEMENT HELPERS</a>
            
            
          </h3>

          <div class="excerpt">
            How to use all the skill in a team to improve your project
	    
          </div>
	  
